  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "To address this gap, we conducted an action research project with the goal of developing theories about learning and teaching processes in the field of AI/ML in order to improve teaching on an empirical basis.",
    "In our national context (Bavaria, Germany), AI was introduced within a mandatory computer science subject for all high school students in year 11 (Jetzinger et al., 2024).",
    "Within the curriculum, in about 16 lessons, the students learn about basic ideas of AI methods, specific algorithms (such as decision tree learning and artificial neural networks), discuss challenges for our society, and train their own AI/ML models.",
    "In our first action research cycle, we particularly focused on students' (AI-specific) learning difficulties.",
    "To this end, the 10 computer science teachers who participated in the project reported their lesson plans and brief reflections on each lesson."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "In our national context (Bavaria, Germany), AI was introduced within a mandatory computer science subject for all high school students in year 11 (Jetzinger et al., 2024)."
  ]
